template.en:
Hi,

You've been invited to access the Parent Portal for {centerName}.

Portal link: {portalUrl}
Login email: {parentEmail}

To sign in, open the portal link and enter your email. We'll send a secure sign-in link to your inbox.

If anything looks incorrect (missing students or sessions), please contact your center admin for help.

template.zhCN:
您好，

您已被邀请访问 {centerName} 的家长端。

链接:{portalUrl}
登录邮箱:{parentEmail}

请打开链接并输入您的邮箱。我们会向您的邮箱发送安全的登录链接。

如信息有误(孩子或课程缺失），请联系校区管理员协助处理。
